   TEXAS: Manager Johnny Oates faxed congratulations to Cal Ripken
on Sunday in recognition of Rikpen's 3,000th hit on Saturday night.
Oates managed Ripken from 1991-94. ... Left-hander Justin Thompson
will make his next rehab start for Tulsa of the Texas League on
Thursday. Thompson started the season on the 15-day disabled list
following left shoulder surgery on Aug. 27, 1999 while a member of
the Detroit Tigers. Thompson threw 75 pitches on Saturday in a
rehab start for Port Charlotte of the Florida State League and
experienced no physical problems.
