   CHICAGO WHITE SOX: The White Sox reinstated OF Jeff Liefer from
the 15-day DL and optioned him to Triple-A Charlotte. Liefer was
placed on the DL March 25 with a partial tear of the posterior
cruciate ligament in his left knee. ... Over the last six games,
the White Sox pitchers have compiled a 3.34 ERA (21 earned runs in
56 2/3 innings) compared to a 6.90 ERA in their first seven games.
